Caching module for PocketFlow

Provides in-memory and persistent caching for LLM responses, embeddings, and other expensive operations.

Types

Cache = ref object
  store*: TableRef[string, CacheEntry]
  maxSize*: int
  defaultTtl*: int
CacheEntry = object
  value*: JsonNode
  timestamp*: Time
  ttlSeconds*: int

Vars

globalCache = newCache(10000, 3600)
